cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR. 

The paper deals with the problem of person re-identification, which is a subfield of computer vision. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also uses deep learning techniques, which makes cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) likely sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves the use of semantic-components and color-texture distributions, which suggests the possibility of it being categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
